an class="_ _8"></span>却从来没有心理准备。<span class="_ _8"></span>甚至有些人</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2a8 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">连想都不敢想，<span class="_ _6"></span>比如自己死了怎么办？突然生病怎么办？这</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2a9 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">些表面上看起来不吉祥，<span class="_ _7"></span>但却是每个人必须要面对的，<span class="_ _7"></span>想逃</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2aa ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">避也是不可能的。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
